</ul><hr id="hr7"><h2 id="the-sisters-grimm-october-3"><a href="https://apple.co/4nxNaro" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Sisters Grimm</a> (October 3)</h2>
<p id="p8">Also debuting on October 3rd is &ldquo;The Sisters Grimm,&rdquo; a new animated series that follows two orphaned sisters who navigate a town packed with people from fantasy and fairy tale stories. The series is based on <a href="https://apple.co/4ntJRBo" rel="noopener noreferrer">Michael Buckley&rsquo;s bestselling book series</a> and features the voices of Ariel Winter as Sabrina and Leah Newman as Daphne. The series blends discovery, fantasy and adventure designed to appeal to all ages.</p>
