</ul><hr id="hr17"><h2 id="loot-season-3-october-15"><a href="https://apple.co/4pMexPQ" rel="noopener noreferrer">Loot, Season 3</a> (October 15)</h2>
<p id="p18">Loot is one of my favorite Apple TV+ comedies. Now in its third season, the series returns on October 15th. In season three, Maya Rudolph&rsquo;s Molly Wells and her assistant head to a remote island to embark on what will be a 10-episode season that airs on Wednesdays.</p>
