</ul><hr id="hr32"><h2 id="down-cemetery-road-october-29"><a href="https://apple.co/46GqMVy" rel="noopener noreferrer">Down Cemetery Road</a> (October 29)</h2>
<p id="p33">Down Cemetery Road is an eight-episode thriller written by Morwenna Banks, who wrote <a href="https://apple.co/4o2gEO6" rel="noopener noreferrer">Slow Horses</a>, one of my all-time favorite shows, for Apple TV+. The series is based on <a href="https://apple.co/48aTnos" rel="noopener noreferrer">the book of the same name by Mick Herron</a> who also wrote the Slow Horses book series. The story follows the disappearance of a girl from an Oxford suburb after a house explosion. The series, which stars Emma Thompson and Ruth Wilson promises to be an exciting conspiratorial story full of twists and turns, which is the sort of show I love.</p>
